snippet: Olesen had a double bogey on the second hole and a bogey on the third but recovered for a one-under-par 71 to hold off Brooks Koepka (67), who tied for second with Chris Stroud (68).
abstract: Thorbjorn Olesen wins Alfred Dunhill Links Championship by two shots.
lead_paragraph: Olesen had a double bogey on the second hole and a bogey on the third but recovered for a one-under-par 71 to hold off Brooks Koepka (67), who tied for second with Chris Stroud (68).

headline.main: Thorbjorn Olesen Holds On for Title
